      <title>由于未平仓合约下降，可可豆价格从历史高位下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/cocoa-extends-rally-to-record-as-dry-weather-adds-to-supply-woes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[可可期货在周二早些时候创下新高后下跌。今年令人眼花缭乱的上涨加上未平仓合约的减少，使得市场更容易受到波动的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/cocoa-extends-rally-to-record-as-dry-weather-adds-to-supply-woes</guid>
